Class Oml2Dot

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.util.Switch<Boolean>
io.opencaesar.oml.util.OmlSwitch<Boolean>
com.plantoml.plantomlserver.translator.Oml2Dot
public class Oml2Dot extends io.opencaesar.oml.util.OmlSwitch<Boolean>
Converts Ontological Modeling Language (OML) elements to DOT format for graph visualization.

This class traverses OML elements and constructs a graph representation using the DOT language, suitable for rendering with Graphviz.

    • pascalCaseToSpaced

      public String pascalCaseToSpaced(String str)
      Converts a PascalCase string to a spaced lowercase string.

      This method is useful for converting class or type names following the PascalCase convention into a more readable spaced lowercase format. It inserts a space before each uppercase letter and converts the entire string to lowercase.

      Parameters:
      str - The PascalCase string to be converted.
      Returns:
      The spaced lowercase string.
